{"tid":646924,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"視察工程新橋突坍塌　菲律賓官員群當場墜海","createTime":"2018-04-29T12:36:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-29T16:04:07.000Z","uid":32938,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"7f2d0f76eaf02a8d4ea3138dfe90743046b63c51","tid":646924,"uid":32938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T12:36:54.000Z","msg":"為了迎接官員視察，不少單位經常會做足準備，以展現出最好的一面。不過近日菲律賓卻有受查單位大出包，一群官員在視察難民家園重建工程，不料木橋卻突然坍塌，眾人當場墜落海裡，所幸所有人都僅受到輕傷。<br />\n<br />\n據外媒報導，該起事件發生在菲律賓三寶顏市，當地時間26日，市長薩拉扎（Maria Isabelle Climaco-Salazar）陪同眾議院住房與城市發展委員會主席貝尼特斯（Alfonso Benitez）、眾議員洛布雷加特（Celso Lobregat）等官員前往該市一處政府為難民興建的社區視察重建工程，沒想到一行人走上一座新蓋的木橋時，橋竟不堪負荷直接坍塌，眾人當場墜落海裡，所幸事發地點位在海水不深的岸邊，官員們在軍警的協助下順利回到岸上，所有人僅受輕傷並無大礙。<br />\n<br />\n對此，薩拉扎表示「真不希望這種事發生，我們倒成了這些不合格建築材料與工程的第一個受害者。」貝尼特斯隨後也在臉書發文表示，這意外顯示難民的住屋不符合標準，憂心他們恐受到二度傷害，直呼「搞不好在戰火中倖存的人會死在政府為他們興建的房屋內」，表示將對此工程展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/HpoqInI5Ces\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FHpoqInI5Ces&d=AXSC5AwpE0WKf1GhavFs9ZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=e12eca71\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/HpoqInI5Ces</a>"},{"pid":"c63e70665bd9b5acd67dd40236bf85d2b33ba066","tid":646924,"uid":1082,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T12:44:20.000Z","msg":"希望港珠澳都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"939d478bd4441822e66cbd150bc02da471e6234b","tid":646924,"uid":176366,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"c63e70665bd9b5acd67dd40236bf85d2b33ba066","tid":646924,"uid":1082,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T12:44:20.000Z","msg":"希望港珠澳都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T12:52:30.000Z","msg":"傻啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n班高官只會搭直昇機視察"},{"pid":"71540702c9f4efcd1e96458a277acb55ced0febf","tid":646924,"uid":63350,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"939d478bd4441822e66cbd150bc02da471e6234b","tid":646924,"uid":176366,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"c63e70665bd9b5acd67dd40236bf85d2b33ba066","tid":646924,"uid":1082,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T12:44:20.000Z","msg":"希望港珠澳都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T12:52:30.000Z","msg":"傻啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n班高官只會搭直昇機視察"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T12:54:17.000Z","msg":"墜機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"690798786f9e8b33a48ae73bf26e641603ce2881","tid":646924,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T12:57:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6be20dc48b47f755b1fbe4851e64d3d12093d263","tid":646924,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T12:59:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e6ac00e7a0971d47a2653b8d6bfc5600999cce4","tid":646924,"uid":41375,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T13:01:06.000Z","msg":"整人節目<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dd646055e1a097b413b6492d52ca1f5d9eae5b4","tid":646924,"uid":19218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"